text: Corey Alan Stewart (born August 1, 1968) is an American lawyer and Republican politician. Stewart is the Chairman of the Prince William Board of County Supervisors. He studied at Georgetown University and at William Mitchell College of Law. He was elected to the Board of County Supervisors in 2003. In July 2017, Stewart announced his candidacy for U.S. Senate. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official Website * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Virginia Category:People from Duluth, Minnesota Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
